isp-tools (1.1.0) stable; urgency=medium

  * Fix blocknet: actually block resolved customer IPs and report real counts
  * Fix unblocknet: label + overdue-invoice driven flow, removes ODPOJENO label
  * Fix CWD-relative autoload path in BlockNet/UnblockNet
  * SubVersioner preserves original speed as 'orig=' comment token and prefers
    the {code:NNNNN} hosts convention when resolving customer IPs
  * Implement Pipeline B: abraflexi-match-received-payment (exit 2 = unmatched),
    abraflexi-potvrzeni-prijeti-uhrady (confirmation with invoice PDF),
    abraflexi-potvrzeni-prijeti-bankovni-platby (unmatched payment notice)
  * Add MultiFlexi app definitions for the three Pipeline B tools
  * Install SpojeNet PSR-4 classes into /usr/share/php/isp-tools/SpojeNet
  * Note: rename LABEL_NODISCONNECTED to LABEL_NODISCONNECT in deployed .env
    files (the old key was never read; the NEODPOJOVAT default applied)

 -- Vítězslav Dvořák <info@vitexsoftware.cz>  Thu, 02 Jul 2026 00:00:00 +0200

isp-tools (1.0.0) stable; urgency=medium

  * Initial Debian packaging
  * Add abraflexi-mark-defaulters: bridge UPOMINKA3 → ODPOJENO for internet customers
  * Add MultiFlexi app definitions for mark-defaulters, blocknet, unblocknet
  * Filter disconnection by INET_CONTRACT_TYPE (typSmlouvy.INTERNET)
  * Document Pipeline A and Pipeline B event rules in README

